@chapter Builtin Action Agents

@menu
* builtin ra_flag_agent::         sets a true/false integer target
* builtin ra_int_agent::          sets an integer target
* builtin ra_string_agent::       sets a const char* target
* builtin ra_show_help_agent::    shows a help display
* builtin ra_show_values_agent::  shows the printable option values
@end menu

@node builtin ra_flag_agent
@section builtin ra_flag_agent

@table @emph

@item target
Target must be an integer, initialized to 0 (false).
@item writer
When invoked, this raAgent writer will set the @emph{target}
value to 1 (true).
@item reader
When invoked, this raAgent will return @emph{false} if the
the value of @emph{target} is 0, and will return @emph{true}
otherwise.
@end table

